# Armin Lišić — Black & White Web Portfolio
Live Version: (add your deployed link here)
Author: https://github.com/Armin-000

A clean, minimalistic, black & white portfolio built with modern UI patterns, floating animations, smooth scroll interactions, and elegant section structure.  
It presents my work, projects, tech stack, and a featured case study: Cochlear Nucleus.

---

## Why Black & White?

No distraction.  
No noise.  
Just clean structure + controlled animations + perfect clarity.

The entire portfolio is focused on:
- smooth micro-interactions  
- premium typography  
- floating arrow animations  
- moving background lines  
- elegant section flow  
- strong UX hierarchy  

Everything is designed to feel calm, sharp, and professional.

---

## Structure of the Portfolio

### Home (Hero)
- Intro text  
- Orbit animation with cards  
- Smooth reveal  
- Scroll indicator  

### About Me
- Profile and philosophy  
- Workflow principles  
- Tag list  
- Professional timeline  

### Featured Project — Cochlear Nucleus
A case-study style section:
- project purpose  
- UX structure  
- UI decisions  
- technical stack  
- metrics and layout  

### Projects
Showcase of selected projects:
- Cochlear Nucleus  
- Car Dealership Platform  
- Future project slot  
- Each with GitHub links  

### Tech Stack
Organized into:
- Frontend  
- Backend & databases  
- Tools & mindset  

### Contact
Includes:
- Email  
- GitHub  
- Location  
- Demo contact form  

---

## Technologies

### Frontend
- HTML5  
- CSS3 (grid, flex, animations)  
- JavaScript (ES6+)  
- Reveal animations  
- Custom parallax effects  

### Tools
- Google Fonts (Inter, Playfair Display)  
- Font Awesome Icons  
- GitHub Pages (optional hosting)  

